//private Boolean isActive =false ---> is this true


@RstController --> used for creating rest api layer /bean of class by container
@Autowired --> we are asking object of required class
@GetMapping --> To Get data from server
@PostMapping --> To add data to server
//@PutMapping
@PatchMapping-->used to partially update data
@DeleteMapping-->used to delete data
@RequiredArgConstructor --> used when we are not using @Autowired annotation

@Data-->to generate getter,setter,toString and equalAndHashCode
@Id--> primary key in table
@GeneratedValue -->used to tell to how to generate the value for primary key
@AllArgConstructor-->Create All Arg. Constructor
@NoArgConstructor --> Create No Arg.Constructor
@Table --> used to tell table name in database
@Entity --> Indicate entity class
@RequestHeader--> when passing parameter in header  of request
@PathVariable --> when passing variable in url of request
@RequestBody --> passing parameters in body of request

@Service --> indicate service layer and create bean of service class in container
@Repository -->indicate repository class and create bean by spring boot container .
@slf4j --> To display log on console

@ExceptionHandler ---> used with method which indicate exception which we are going to handle.
@RestControllerAdvice --> used with class which is handling exception